</ul>
<p><em> </em><strong>Rachel&#8217;s Simple Seasoning (RSS) or My Favorite Seasoning Blend for Meat </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>1/4 C salt</li>
<li>1/4 C Garlic Powder</li>
<li>1 Tbsp Onion Powder</li>
<li>1 Tbsp Paprika</li>
<li>1/4 C Coarsely Ground Pepper</li>
<li>1 tsp Ground Mustard</li>
<li>1 tsp Comino (Cumin)</li>
<li>1 tsp cayenne</li>
<li>dash cinnamon</li>
</ul>
<p><em>these are all full measurements</em></p>
<p><em><strong>Congratulations to our winner!!  Tammy Munson commenter #25</strong></em></p>
